title: Twitter/Social Accounts to be managed by Telegram Admins
body:
This is a proposal to hand over management of the Twitter/Social Accounts to one of the Telegram admins potentially, Moon_way, to increase marketing and awareness of this great project?

King Frog and Prince Frog are busy with the development side of things, I think that Moon-way could do a good job of marketing and spreading awareness of the FrogDAO Project using simple posts on Twitter/Reddit and other social channels.

This will improve the presence of this project - both to investors and projects looking for incubator platforms.
choices: No, keep social management as is
author: 0x9D2Cb99B6e81C99f708E75bBEc35C8bEA512766e
